name: The Gook Gook Family
description: This is my first drop in H=N. When I first saw this website, I think of hen so I drew a hen and her 5 eggs in paper cut style. In Thai when we call chicken to come for you. We use voice "Gook Gook" come here baby so I hope When Gook Gook family stay with you. She and her babies will bring luck for you.Thank you in advance for adopting Gook Gook family.
